'''''The Nest of the Turtledove''''' ({{lang-uk|'''Гніздо горлиці'''}}) is a 2016 Ukrainian [[drama film]] directed by [[Taras Tkachenko]].<ref name="review">{{cite web|url=http://odessareview.com/nest-turtledove/ |title=OIFF Update: "The Nest of the Turtledove" |work=Odessa Review |date=26 July 2016 |accessdate=31 August 2016}}</ref> It was named as one of three films shortlisted as the Ukrainian submission for the [[Academy Award for Best Foreign Language Film]], but it was not selected.<ref name="Ukraine">{{cite web|url=http://life.pravda.com.ua/culture/2016/08/31/217458/ |title=Обрано три фільми-кандидати на "Оскар" від України |work=[[Ukrayinska Pravda]] |language=Ukrainian |date=31 August 2016 |accessdate=31 August 2016}}</ref>
